	Thanks goes to Andrew Simpson (andrewsimpson) for reporting this.

2003-03-05 21:00  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* ChangeLog:

	Latest ChangeLog entries.

2003-03-05 20:18  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* VERSION:

	This is version 2.1.1.

2003-03-05 20:02  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* ChangeLog:

	Most significant entries in the ChangeLog since 2.1.0:

	* New German translation by Konrad Tadesse.  * Configuration
	problem in output modules (bug #613963) fixed.	* Added a simple
	page to help people test their connectivity.  * The arrows that
	show the wind direction can be reversed.

2003-03-05 19:56  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* base_object.php:

	This verbosity-thing isn't really used... There's no real reason to
	make an extra member variable just to hold this, when we have it as
	$this->properties['verbosity'].

2003-03-05 19:53  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* output/: pw_images.php, pw_output.php, pw_text.php:

	This should fix bug #613963 at SourceForge. The problem was, that
	pw_text_xx and pw_images always used the default settings, and
	refused to react to settings in the phpweather object they used.

	You can now control things by first setting defaults in
	defaults.php, second by giving the phpweather object an array with
	settings when it's created, and third by overriding the previous
	settings by giving pw_text_xx or pw_images an array with settings
	upon creation.

2003-03-05 18:39  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* output/pw_text_de.php:

	Small fixes from Konrad Tadesse.

2003-03-04 14:36  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* output/pw_text_de.php, AUTHORS:

	Super! A German translation from Konrad Tadesse.

2003-01-21 22:27  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* defaults-dist.php, output/pw_images.php:

	Rudy Boedts wanted the direction of the arrows changed, so this is
	now configurable through the reverse_dir option.

2003-01-21 22:25  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* make-release.sh, update-changelog.sh:

	A script to generate the ChangeLog with consistent options.

2003-01-16 12:52  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* config/connectivity_test.php:

	Updated relative links to stylesheet and logo.

2003-01-16 12:50  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* config/: connectivity_test.php, index.php:

	Added a simple page to help people test if they can connect to the
	NWS.

2002-12-28 14:25  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* ChangeLog:

	Hmm, this should be the last changes - here comes 2.1.0!

2002-12-28 14:22  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* index.php:

	Added link to the configuration tools.

2002-12-28 14:15  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* config/: make_config.php, pw_optiongroup.php:

	Added extra 'Update options' buttons and reformatted the bottom
	'Download the Configuration' bottom so that value attribute is no
	longer split between two lines - this confused Mozilla.

2002-12-28 14:13  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* doc/: .cvsignore, phpweather.dvi, phpweather.html,
	phpweather.info, phpweather.info-1, phpweather.info-2,
	phpweather.pdf, phpweather.ps, phpweather.txt, src/phpweather.texi:

	Fixed bad reference and regenerated documentation. The generated
	documentation should probably not be in CVS at all, but we'll deal
	with that later.

2002-12-28 13:41  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* ChangeLog:

	Updated with changes from 2.0.0 to 2.1.0.

