	Oops. I think this was my first contribution to the project, and
	it's taken this long to spot the problem with it :)

2002-10-24 15:54  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* AUTHORS, output/pw_text_fr.php:

	Cool - a French translation thanks to Guillaume Petit
	<gpetit@fr.st>!

2002-10-20 15:57  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* output/: pw_text.php, pw_text_da.php, pw_text_en.php,
	pw_text_no.php:

	Fix for a problem found by Sean <sean@arrowsmith.biz>. The problem
	was, that the report said 'There were The sky was overcast...' when
	we had a OVC cloud group. This should fix that problem.

	I've also changed the translation of 'cloud_vertical_visibility' so
	that it fits into the 'There was ...' part. I've updated the
	English, Danish ans Norwegian translations.

2002-10-01 19:03  Ondrej Jombik   <nepto@pobox.sk>

	* output/pw_text_cs.php:

	Little fix in function parse_cloud_group($cloud_group).  Removed
	unneccessary test metars from the bottom of file.

