2002-05-18 09:20  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* phpweather.php:

	It seams that pow() cannot handle floats passed to it as strings,
	at least not in PHP 4.2.0 at gimpster.com. The strange thing is
	that it works in PHP 4.1.2 at my local machine.

2002-05-18 08:39  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* phpweather.php:

	When the windchill and heatindex was calculated, the temperature
	and windspeed was compared to strings and not integers.

	I also re-indented some of the code.

