2002-03-17 14:13  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

	* ChangeLog, usermap:

	Updated ChangeLog and added iridium to the usermappings.

	By the way, what do people think about having their email-addresses
	written all over the place without any SPAM-protection?

	I have no problem with this myself, as my email-address is SPAM-
	protected by a program called TMDA, but it just occurred to me that
	some of you might have tied to keep your address 'secret' and then
	I just write it all over the place...

	In short: feel free to edit usermap and AUTHORS if you want the
	info to be different than what I've made.

2002-03-17 14:06  Martin Geisler  <gimpster@gimpster.com>

