	pw_text_en.php, pw_text_hu.php, pw_text_no.php:

	The new output modules. pw_text does that locale_common did before,
	and pw_text_xx are the localized version of the class. pw_images is
	new - it selects suitable images for display with or instead of the
	textual report.

